MATCH_TOOL: Edit|Write
MATCH_PATTERN: react|REACT|reaction|Reaction
ADVISORY: |
  Vivid's double-tap reactions are VISUAL ONLY — local React state for 800ms, no server
  round-trip, no persistence. Events.Social.REACT does NOT exist yet in shared-types.
  ChannelCapability already includes 'REACTIONS' as a value and MAIN is initialized with
  capabilities: ['CHAT', 'REACTIONS'], but no server handler processes reaction events.
  To add persistent reactions: add event to shared-types, add L3 handler, store reactions
  as metadata on ChatMessage objects in chatLog, deliver via SYNC on each message.
